SUMMARY:WINEROAD Barrel Tasting Weekend
DESCRIPTION:In celebration of its 50th Anniversary\, Wine Road’s signature Barrel Weekend returns for a full weekend experience.    A cherished tradition of the Wine Road\, Barrel Weekend invites guests to sample wines straight from the barrel\, just as the winemaker does. Step into the cellar\, meet the vintners\, and gain insight into their craft and philosophy. While the focus is on wine rather than food pairings\, guests are encouraged to pack a picnic and enjoy lunch on the beautiful winery grounds. In addition to barrel tastings\, many wineries will pour current releases ready to enjoy\, and select locations may offer rare library wines offering a unique chance to experience the past\, present\, and future of winemaking in one immersive weekend. Single-day tickets are not available; groups of eight or more are not permitted.  
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/wineroad-barrel-tasting-weekend/
LOCATION:783 Broadway, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
GEO:-122.459041;38.286879
CATEGORIES:Celebration,Drink,Sonoma County,Wine
