SUMMARY:Sonoma Epicurean - Epic Party at Walt Wines
DESCRIPTION:Join WALT Wines at Sonoma Epicurean’s Epic Party\, a high-energy kickoff celebration at Bacchus Landing. Part of the signature Sonoma Epicurean series\, the weekend showcases curated\, hands-on experiences with award-winning chefs\, local artisans\, and world-class vintners.    The Epic Party sets the tone with a lively\, welcoming atmosphere where guests can circulate freely\, tasting exceptional wines and savoring culinary bites from Sonoma’s talented chefs and producers. It’s a relaxed\, social evening designed for connection\, discovery\, and celebration—bringing together an engaged\, wine-loving audience in one vibrant setting.    Proceeds from Sonoma Epicurean support the V Foundation for Cancer Research\, helping fund groundbreaking cancer research and related programs.
URL:https://www.sonoma.com/event/sonoma-epicurean-epic-party-at-walt-wines/
LOCATION:380 First Street West, Sonoma, CA, 95476, United States
GEO:-122.4583304;38.294346
